Info: Due to technical difficulties, the platform that was supposed to fly Taylor from Main Stage to B-Stage during "Delicate" was stuck in mid-air. She landed on Main Stage and sang "Our Song" a cappella to fill the time. She then took the Snake Skeleton platform (that usually flies her from C-Stage to Main Stage during "Bad Blood") to the C-Stage while singing "Wildest Dreams" a cappella. Because of that, Taylor did not walk through the crowd before "Blank Space", like she usually does. Fans reported that, for the third time (first in Chicago night 2, and second London night 1), a film crew was present, filming at the venue.
